g.text: An Operational System of Record is a foundational, interconnected platform that brings teams together, streamlines processes, reveals key business insights, and provides all the key capabilities you need to successfully operate your services organization in the modern services economy

An Operational System of Record provides detailed forecasting on resources, revenue, and margins so you can dial in projections and plan with precision to help your people and projects succeed. Greater vision and insight leads to improved decision-making and predictability in your business.
